1. Login page
    +activity,
    +xml,
    +onClick handler,

OnClick - go by api, check if user in db,
            -yes -> login, save user data in preferences
            -no -> Alert "Wrong user data", suggest to sing up

login api steps:
    + go to server
    + find user with email
    + check if password correct
    + return success or throw an exception

Error handling
    + no connection;
    + 500 error;
    + 400 error;

on success:
    + put data in sqlite
    + save email and password to the preferences (check on app start and auto login)
    + check preferences on app start
    + login the system to the main page
    - add spinning progress bar

+ add log out item in menu
+ delete preferences when log_out



------Global-------

*While launching - check preferences
*Redirect from main menu if no user found

